That's what I say. I used to go to these dances and things and meet the girls.

00:42:54.140 --> 00:42:57.140
And my mother didn't, she used to let me go.

00:42:57.140 --> 00:43:02.140
And of course I met my husband and he didn't care if I had to and that was terrible really.

00:43:02.140 --> 00:43:07.140
Because if a son of mine had come home and said I've met this girl with TB, I'd have gone.

00:43:07.140 --> 00:43:12.140
But I think most people had it. I know it sounds awful, but it was rife.

00:43:12.140 --> 00:43:18.140
Most families had someone or knew someone or it was terrible.

00:43:18.140 --> 00:43:21.140
But I did say I'm not going in hospital at all.

00:43:21.140 --> 00:43:23.140
Because there's no cure anyway.

00:43:23.140 --> 00:43:29.140
My father said you keep away from that hospital, you'll catch it worse off the others and all that nonsense.

00:43:29.140 --> 00:43:36.140
But then this tablets come out that you could take.

00:43:36.140 --> 00:43:43.140
There was probably a cure for some people, but by the time it got to the public, I was so ill.

00:43:43.140 --> 00:43:45.140
They gave me these tablets and I was so ill.

00:43:45.140 --> 00:43:50.140
So they took the tablets off me and I didn't take them.

00:43:51.140 --> 00:43:54.140
And then I met my husband, got married.

00:43:54.140 --> 00:44:00.140
And he had a job in Bristol and it wasn't so bad in Bristol, the TB.

00:44:00.140 --> 00:44:08.140
Because I was checking up on my chest, I went for an x-ray and he said you'd better come in and have this stuff.

00:44:08.140 --> 00:44:13.140
And I said I can't take it because it won't work on me, I was too ill.

00:44:13.140 --> 00:44:15.140
And he said we'll desensitise you.

00:44:15.140 --> 00:44:17.140
And I said what's that?

00:44:17.140 --> 00:44:22.140
And he said we'll give you the tiniest spot, like a pinhead of it.

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:25.140
And then we'll increase it so gradually your body won't know you're out.

00:44:25.140 --> 00:44:28.140
And he done it and I cured and it worked.

00:44:28.140 --> 00:44:31.140
And I went in, it was hellish going in mind.

00:44:31.140 --> 00:44:33.140
Oh it was awful.

00:44:33.140 --> 00:44:39.140
And there was people being operated on, they'd lungs out, it was terrible in there, in south medium Bristol.

00:44:39.140 --> 00:44:42.140
And he'd give me the little bit, it must have been a week.

00:44:42.140 --> 00:44:45.140
I didn't know when he was giving it to me.

00:44:45.140 --> 00:44:49.140
And they got me on it and it worked.

00:44:49.140 --> 00:44:51.140
So they got rid of it for me.

00:44:51.140 --> 00:44:52.140
Right.

00:44:52.140 --> 00:44:56.140
So basically you never went back to work?

00:44:56.140 --> 00:44:58.140
No, no, no.

00:44:58.140 --> 00:44:59.140
Well, erm.

00:44:59.140 --> 00:45:01.140
There you are.

00:45:01.140 --> 00:45:02.140
No, leave, no.

00:45:02.140 --> 00:45:04.140
So, erm.

00:45:04.140 --> 00:45:07.140
So did you enjoy working in the factory?

00:45:07.140 --> 00:45:08.140
I did, yes I did.

00:45:08.140 --> 00:45:10.140
Did you ever find it boring or monotonous?

00:45:10.140 --> 00:45:11.140
No, no, no.

00:45:11.140 --> 00:45:14.140
No, the time went so quick, the clock was so quick.

00:45:14.140 --> 00:45:15.140
Oh right.

00:45:15.140 --> 00:45:16.140
Yeah.

00:45:16.140 --> 00:45:23.140
So, did you keep in contact with your former workmates?

00:45:23.140 --> 00:45:26.140
Well, when I got married I moved to Bristol.

00:45:26.140 --> 00:45:29.140
So I was up there ten years, so I did lose.

00:45:29.140 --> 00:45:34.140
But I'm still writing to girls in school who was in my class.

00:45:34.140 --> 00:45:41.140
And this one, Betsy I told you, she worked with me.

00:45:41.140 --> 00:45:43.140
And she sent me a Christmas card.

00:45:43.140 --> 00:45:44.140
Yes.

00:45:44.140 --> 00:45:49.140
So I imagine if you get in touch I should imagine she'll remember what I sent.

00:45:49.140 --> 00:45:54.140
And looking back now then, how do you feel about the time you worked?

00:45:54.140 --> 00:45:56.140
I loved it.

00:45:56.140 --> 00:45:58.140
I loved it.

00:45:58.140 --> 00:45:59.140
Great.

00:45:59.140 --> 00:46:00.140
Thank you very much.

00:46:00.140 --> 00:46:01.140
Oh.

